<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Password Change Successful</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f4; color: #1a1a1a; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background-color: #16a34a; padding: 40px 40px 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .header .logo span { color: #bbf7d0; }
    .header .tagline { font-size: 13px; color: #bbf7d0; margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #15803d 0%, #16a34a 50%, #22c55e 100%); padding: 36px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .hero .emoji { font-size: 48px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.3; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #bbf7d0; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body p { font-size: 15px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .body p strong { color: #16a34a; }
    .info-card { background-color: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0; border-left: 4px solid #16a34a; }
    .info-card .label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #16a34a; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .info-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .info-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .info-icon { font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .info-text { font-size: 14px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.5; }
    .warning-card { background-color: #fff7ed; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 24px 0; border-left: 4px solid #f97316; }
    .warning-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 0; line-height: 1.7; }
    .warning-card p strong { color: #c2410c; }
    .cta-wrapper { text-align: center; margin: 32px 0 8px; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #16a34a; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; padding: 14px 40px; border-radius: 50px; letter-spacing: 0.3px; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.35); }
    .divider { height: 1px; background-color: #e5e7eb; margin: 32px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 28px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .footer p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .footer a { color: #16a34a; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
    .footer .social { margin: 14px 0 10px; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">Amebo<span>Naija</span></div>
      <div class="tagline">Nigeria's #1 Gist Hub</div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero">
      <span class="emoji">🔐</span>
      <h1>Password change <span>successful!</span></h1>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p>
        Hi <strong><%= firstName %></strong>, your password has been successfully change. You can now log in to your Amebo Naija account with your new password.
      </p>

      <div class="info-card">
        <p class="label">What just happened</p>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-icon">✅</span>
          <span class="info-text">Your password was changed successfully</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-icon">🕐</span>
          <span class="info-text">Time: <%= new Date().toUTCString() %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-icon">📧</span>
          <span class="info-text">Account: <%= email %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="warning-card">
        <p>⚠️ <strong>Wasn't you?</strong> If you did not request this password change, your account may be at risk. Please contact us immediately or change your password again right away.</p>
      </div>

      <p>
        For your security, we recommend you do not share your password with anyone and use a strong, unique password.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-wrapper">
        <a href="https://amebonaija.vercel.app/login" class="cta-btn">Log In Now →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
        You're receiving this email because a password change was completed on your Amebo Naija account.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="social">🇳🇬</div>
      <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Amebo Naija. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><a href="https://amebonaija.vercel.app">amebonaija.vercel.app</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
